==English==
===Noun===
'''calque''' (''plural'' '''[[calques]]''')
{{wikipedia}}
# A word or phrase that has been translated [[semantically]] from one language for use in another.
# A word-for-word translation of one saying into another. 
#:''The phrase "that goes without saying" is a '''calque''' of the French phrase "ça va sans dire".''
#:'''The word [[watershed]] is a calque from German [[wasserscheid]]

